a.xlink:title: [ StateCheck(Myself,STATE_CHARMED) [ARAN] Look at all th' pretty colors. Real nice, eh?
[[ARAN] 'We must all think for ourselves'. Hey, that be a joke, right? I saw a snake charmer named Monty do that bit once.
[RandomNum(4,4) [PC] Hey, Aran, repeat after me... 'We must all think for ourselves'...
[[ARAN] (*gulp*) Hey, that tastes like chicken. Or anythin' you decide to cook, for that matter.
[RandomNum(4,3)[PC] Drink this cup of mud. It will make you feel better.
[[ARAN] (*swat*) OUCH! Banes Bouncing Buttocks, that bloody well hurt!
[RandomNum(4,2)[PC] Hey you have a fly on your nose. Swat it, quick!
[[ARAN] Absolutely. You can have th' whole purse. O' course, there be naught in it, but I will pay you back th' very second I have the coin.
[RandomNum(4,1)[PC] You owe me money, boyo. Come on, 20 gold, right now.
[[ARAN] I be tryin', but there be too much in th' way. Luckily, your arse be big enough that I don't even have to kneel down...
[RandomNum(4,4)[PC] Now I have you where I want you. Kiss my bottom, sellsword.
[[ARAN] Right, then. I don't rightly think that word means what you think it meanZzzzzzzz... (Thud.)
[RandomNum(4,3)[PC] Go to sleep, Aran, and dream of large women.
[[ARAN] Which head? I'm not rightly equipped for standin' on either... oh! You mean do a hand-stand like one o' them acrobat types! Right, can do. Hold on...~ = ~[ARAN] (*thud*) ...medic...
[RandomNum(4,2)[PC] Hey, Aran, stand on your head.
[[ARAN] Now, I feel a hard pull to do what you just said, an' that be strange, on account o' that be a right nasty way to die. I'm not keen on stickin' blunt objects up there, neither.
[RandomNum(4,1) [PC] Hey, Aran, stick a dagger where the sun doesn't shine.

[[ARAN] No, I feel right fine. I feel a strong compulsion to do anythin' you say, an' your face is surrounded by some right wild colors, but then again, that don't seem no different from an average day.
[[PC] Are you all right? It looks like you have been charmed or something.
[[ARAN] Drama queen tendencies, father issues, cutest little arse you ever did see, an' I wouldn't kick her out o' bed. At least, not right away.
[InParty(Player2) Gender(Player2,FEMALE) !Name(c-aran,Player2) [PC] So, what do you really think of PLAYER2?

[[ARAN] I think she needs a good roll in th' hay, or mayhap some strong drink, or perhaps even a solid knock aside th' head to set her straight. I think I will not be volunteerin' for that job. But you could always order me to...
[InParty(Player3) Gender(Player3,FEMALE) !Name(c-aran,Player3) [PC] So, what do you really think of PLAYER3?
[[ARAN] PLAYER4? I don't rightly know yet. Get her drunk, let her sing some, an' I'll have me some observations to share. What gig do you be auditionin' her for?
[InParty(Player4) Gender(Player4,FEMALE) !Name(c-aran,Player4) [PC] So, what do you really think of PLAYER4?
[[ARAN] Nice tits.
[InParty(Player5) Gender(Player5,FEMALE) !Name(c-aran,Player5) [PC] So, what do you really think of PLAYER5?

[[ARAN] That be strange. I feel a right strong compulsion to say what I think, but somethin' tells me that if I do PLAYER6 will slice my head off. Or you will. Or you both will. I be gettin' a mite bit confused...
[InParty(Player6) Gender(Player6,FEMALE) !Name(c-aran,Player6) [PC] So, what do you really think of PLAYER6?
[[ARAN] Not bad lookin' for an ugly fellow. His kids are goin' to be one hell o' a mess, though.
[InParty(Player2) Gender(Player2,MALE) !Name(c-aran,Player2) [PC] So, what do you really think of PLAYER2?
[[ARAN] Not bad in a fight. Not so hot in th' ladies department, though. An' his farts smell like old feet.
[InParty(Player3) Gender(Player3,MALE) !Name(c-aran,Player3) [PC] So, what do you really think of PLAYER3?
[[ARAN] Makes me a mite jealous, he does. Not many men can snore, belch, an' fart like that, an' to do all three at th' same time, now that takes bloody fine skills, eh?
[InParty(Player4) Gender(Player4,MALE) !Name(c-aran,Player4) [PC] So, what do you really think of PLAYER4?
[[ARAN] I don't. Should I? I mean, he be right fine lookin', but I tend to think o' womenfolk. Why, did he ask about me? What did he say?
[InParty(Player5) Gender(Player5,MALE) !Name(c-aran,Player5) [PC] So, what do you really think of PLAYER5?

[[ARAN] Not th' sharpest o' tacks, though he claims a good bit o' intelligence. What sort o' idiot wanders Toril in th' company o' a mixed group o' adventurers, followin' some young adventurin' Bhaalspawn to certain death an' destruction, probably by a slow an' painful means? I mean, really, come on. Any smart adventurer would say 'Screw this. I'm hittin' th' nearest tavern, an' not leavin' until someone comes up wi' an adventure what don't pit me against opponents what be gods'.
[InParty(Player6) Gender(Player6,MALE) !Name(c-aran,Player6) [PC] So, what do you really think of PLAYER6?
[[ARAN] I think if I hadn't met you, naught but boredom an' ennui would o' happened for me. Well, sometimes I think that. Other times, I'm just starin' at you an' imaginin' you naked.
[Gender(Player1,FEMALE) [PC] So, what do you really think of me?

[[ARAN] I think if I hadn't met you, naught but boredom an' ennui would o' happened for me. Don't rightly know whether to thank you for that, or tell you to stick Helm's Fist up your arse an' give it a good twist.
[Gender(Player1,MALE) [PC] So, what do you really think of me?

[[ARAN] Hey, by the way, your armor be all wrong. I know you be th' scourge o' Faerun, but you don't have to wear your heart on your sleeve, eh? In this case, someone else's, by th' look. Not a great morale boostin' thing, by my account. DO SetGlobal(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,1) SetGlobalTimer(c-aranskin,GLOBAL,FOUR_DAYS)
[HasItemEquiped(LEAT21,Player1) Global(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,0)
[[ARAN] You still be wearin' that Grumbar-lovin' Cyric-blighted armor? Gives me th' chills, it does.
[HasItemEquiped(LEAT21,Player1) Global(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,1) GlobalTimerExpired(c-aranskin,GLOBAL)

[[ARAN] Look, I do a good bit around here, an' I know you be th' leader. I'm just sayin', that armor makes it blighted hard for me to do my job. Th' smell be only part o' it. Shar's Kiss, get rid o' it, eh?
[HasItemEquiped(LEAT21,Player1) Global(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,2) GlobalTimerExpired(c-aranskin,GLOBAL)

[[ARAN] Hey, I don't go around second guessin' you. So if I be sayin' it, you know there be one hells of a lot more people who have noticed. Might fit your ideas, but it be bad tactics to give away your position that way.
[[PC] If it bothers you that much, I will take it off. DO SetGlobal(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,2) SetGlobalTimer(c-aranskin,GLOBAL,FOUR_DAYS)
[[PC] I think it has a great effect on our opponents' morale. You are just going to have to get used to it. DO SetGlobal(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,2) SetGlobalTimer(c-aranskin,GLOBAL,FOUR_DAYS)
[[PC] If I wanted you opinion, I would have asked. DO SetGlobal(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,2) SetGlobalTimer(c-aranskin,GLOBAL,FOUR_DAYS)
[[PC] Shut up, or your ears will add decoration to it. DO SetGlobal(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,2) SetGlobalTimer(c-aranskin,GLOBAL,FOUR_DAYS)
[[ARAN] Cyric's Black Heart, I don't run out on contracts. But you smell worse than a charnelhouse. If I throw up, you will be knowin' why.
[[PC] Or you will run crying like a weakling child, break your contract, and leave?~ DO ~SetGlobal(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,3)
[[PC] Shut up, Aran. I heard you the first two times. I will use what tools I see fit to advance my goals.~ DO ~SetGlobal(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,3)
[[PC] Are you volunteering to add more skin to this armor? Speak again, and I will ~ DO ~SetGlobal(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,3)
[[PC] I may very well take it off. You are useful. But then again, I might put it back on. You will have to get used to it, or leave.~ DO ~SetGlobal(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,3)
[[PC] You do very little, and I am tired of your whining. That is the last warning you will get.~ DO ~SetGlobal(c-arskinarm,LOCALS,3)
